<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_160_r1l9"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> wolfram als Jr vns nehſt vnd yecʒ von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> <expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> vollands </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_160_r1l10"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_160_r1l11"><expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> volland / <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒured geſecʒt / Der hat vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / daʒ der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_160_r1l12">wald mıt ſeınr <expan>ʒugehöru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> ſein kawfts gut ſey <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> auch Jm der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_160_r1l13">. <expan cert="unknown">C .</expan> <expan>Perıngerſtorff<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ʒuu<ex>er</ex>ſprechen</expan> ſtee vnd Jn mıt tur vnd tor beſlıeſſ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_160_r1l14">den kawff er langʒeıt dauor ee der <expan>Perıngſtorff<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan> wurde </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_160_r1l15">getan hab vnd tu auch das <expan>niema<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu fluchſal noch ʒu ſchırm als </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_160_r1l16">er das mıt <expan>ſeıne<ex>n</ex></expan> rechten wol getraw ʒu beweıſen . <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_160_r1l17"><expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır eẅch Jr ſeyt daran . daʒ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> der ſein ledıg vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_160_r1l18">das ſein gekert <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan> . ſo wıſſen wır ʒu <expan>dıſenʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> mıt ewch vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_160_r1l19">dem <expan>gılg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>teynſtorff<ex>er</ex></expan> in ſunderheıt nıht ʒu ſchıken <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> denn guts </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_160_r1l20">denn als wır eẅch vor <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> daʒ wır nıht <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſehen daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_160_r1l21">des Reıchs ſtraſſe ʒu vnd von vns beſchedıgt oder <expan>dernıd<ex>er</ex>gelegt</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_160_r1l22">ſölt <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> . Vnd lat vns von des <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> <expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> vollands </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_160_r1l23">ſache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> antwurt <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> bey dıſem <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_160" id="79r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
